ies viable – 2014’s <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/independent-library-report-for-england\" title=\"\">Independent Library Report</a> advocated a “national digital network for libraries”.<br /><strong>Graham Ullathorne</strong><br /><em>Chesterfield, Derbyshire</em></p> <p><strong><em>• Join the debate – email </em></strong><a href=\"mailto:guardian.letters@theguardian.com\" title=\"\"><strong><em>guardian.letters@theguardian.com</em></strong></a></p>","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/4jbc7","wordcount":"151","thumbnail":"https://media.guim.co.uk/f2f4b9b38262bc2d596cc3f95893fc8164a5d1dc/0_212_4428_2656/500.jpg"},"webUrl":"https://www.theguardian.com/books/2016/may/18/why-we-shouldnt-dismiss-digital-books","apiUrl":"https://content.guardianapis.com/books/2016/may/18/why-we-shouldnt-dismiss-digital-books","sectionName":"Books","elements":[{"id":"f2f4b9b38262bc2d596cc3f95893fc8164a5d1dc","relation":"main","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","file":"https://media.guim.co.uk/f2f4b9b38262bc2d596cc3f95893fc8164a5d1dc/0_212_4428_2656/2000.jpg","typeData":{"copyright":"2012 EyesWideOpen","picdarUrn":"GD*30016642","mediaApiUri":"https://api.media.gutools.co.uk/images/f2f4b9b38262bc2d596cc3f95893fc8164a5d1dc","suppliersReference":"139216356","altText":"A tourist reads a book with an e-reader in Goa, India","caption":"A tourist reads a book with an e-reader in Goa, India. ‘We shouldn’t dismiss advances in modern technology,’ writes Graham Ullathorne.","photographer":"EyesWideOpen","source":"Getty Images","credit":"Photograph: EyesWideOpen/Getty Images","mediaId":"f2f4b9b38262bc2d596cc3f95893fc8164a5d1dc","displayCredit":"true","imageType":"Photograph","secureFile":"https://media.guim.co.uk/f2f4b9b38262bc2d596cc3f95893fc8164a5d1dc/0_212_4428_2656/2000.jpg","width":"2000","height":"1200"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg"},{"type":"image","file":"https://media.guim.co.uk/f2f4b9b38262bc2d596cc3f95893fc8164a5d1dc/0_212_4428_2656/1000.jpg","typeData":{"copyright":"2012 E